text:
So bad, in fact, that the mother of Sean Preston, 11, and Jayden James, 12, has started “taking prenatal vitamins to prepare for pregnancy,” the source dished to RadarOnline.com.

“She is hoping to become pregnant in the very near future and Sam is totally on board with this.”

Since meeting Asghari on the set of “Slumber Party” video, she has gotten into incredinle shape – and doesn’t hesitate to show it off on Instagram!
title: Oh Baby, Baby! Britney Desperate To Get Pregnant With Boytoy Sam Asghari
